Ranger Help for: rest
=====================

SYNTAX:      rest
             rest camp (or: rest home)
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   10
BASE SP:     35 (rest) / 50 (rest camp)
SKILL TYPE:  Cartography

SUMMARY:
Rest has two modes:

REST (heal):
  Find a sheltered spot and rest briefly, recovering HP and SP.
  Must be in the wilderness and not in combat. Healing scales with
  your constitution and wisdom. You will sit down while resting.

REST CAMP / REST HOME (travel):
  Return to your own camp from anywhere. Costs 50 SP. You must
  have a camp established (see 'camp' for setup instructions).
  This is the fastest way to get back to your base.

